Knowledge Manager Notes


Requirements:

Must haves:
 - Add new document
 - Edit document
 - View document
 - Search for document
 - Add, search, and filter by keyword

Should haves:
 - Multiplatform
 - Cloud-based web app
 - Support for text, web, word, pdf, images, epub

Nice to haves:
 - Auto keyword extraction
 - Auto topic extraction
 - Text extraction from image
 - Document location bookmarks
 - Mobile app





Adding document:
	- Create a folder if it doesn't exist
	- Ask for document name
	- Add new .txt document with provided name to the folder if it doesn't exist already, otherwise raise a warning
	- Start taking input to add to the document